{"tid":2042023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署署長胡英明：反中亂港分子連番衝擊香港的法治","createTime":"2020-05-29T15:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T15:03:23.000Z","uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42af31130a8be8dff8d9915c73823d3b156d5d06","tid":2042023,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/30414/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-30414/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F30414%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-30414%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=e9d844ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/30414/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-30414/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n【港版國安法】鄧炳強央視專訪：立法能打擊港獨 與律政司緊密溝通確保法例有效實施<br />\n<br />\n懲教署署長胡英明表示，反中亂港分子連番衝擊香港的法治，破壞社會秩序已經一年時間了，香港的法治、經濟、民生和國際形象，已經受到嚴重影響，同時衝擊「一國兩制」，還有香港的繁榮穩定，在這個時候立法「對香港來說是必須的，也是應該的」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警甴拘捕、紅官唔批保釋、入獄虐待一條龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576ad9e117c646be84251ddc9d545271dd85f04b","tid":2042023,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"高可晴"},{"pid":"ed0001b185c7b6a5ef0999b36b3634ef9689752c","tid":2042023,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"5個署長出哂黎啦<br />\n不過普通話就"}]}